title: Character_2_Question
---
<<SwitchScene Doorway>>
<<set $character_id to 2>>
// do load character
<<detour Character_Load>>
<<set $visited_num to 0>>

{$character_name} :你好呀！我是芙蕾雅，独立调查员！你的旅馆在环境读数上显示为异常安全区，这太有趣了！能让我进来研究一下吗？我会付钱的！
<<jump Character_2_RealQuestions>>
===

title: Character_2_RealQuestions
